Intu Properties on Thursday announced the appointment of Barbara Gibbes as interim CFO with effect from April 29. Gibbes joined Intu as FD in January 2017. The process to recruit a permanent CFO has started and will include internal and external candidates. Hugo Ford, general counsel and group treasurer will continue to report to Matthew Roberts, CE designate, on all financing and treasury matters. JSE-listed Intu owns and manages shopping centres in the UK.